  "texts": [
    "The breast ultrasound images dataset (BUSI) which contains 780 images collected from 600 female patients between the ages of 25 and 75 in 2018, with a resolution of 500 Â 500 pixels.",
    "These images are divided into three categories: normal (133), malignant (210), and benign (437).",
    "Ground truth images are also available for use in image segmentation or detection.",
    "The BUSI dataset is an important tool for the classification of breast cancer in deep learning.",
    "Figure 5 illustrates some examples from the BUSI dataset."
  ]
}